  "title": "Permanent Part Time Beauty Advisor",
  "description": "<p><strong>To support Shilla’s rapid expansion in Singapore, we are recruiting for Permanent Part Time Beauty Advisors to join our growing family.</strong></p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Employment type:</strong> Permanent Part Time Beauty Advisor</p><p><strong>Duration:</strong> 22 hrs per week (Exclude break)</p><p><strong>Working days:</strong> 3-4 days per week</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>We provide excellent training and career progression opportunity.</strong></p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Be a Shilla ambassador and portray a professional and customer oriented image at all times.</li><li>Welcome every customer and elevate customer service experience through good customer service, sharing of solid product knowledge and expertise.</li><li>Recognize sale opportunities when dealing with customers and be able to capitalize on upselling / cross presentation of items or services at point of service.</li><li>Perform inventory replenishment as and when required.</li><li>Maintain basic housekeeping and abide to all operation procedures.</li><li>Operate POS cash register and handle various mode of payment.</li><li>Any other duties as per assigned</li></ul><p><strong>(Only short-listed candidates will be notified)</strong></p><p><br /></p>",
