    "description": "<p>Shilla Duty Free, an affiliate of Samsung Group is a leading global travel retailer offering quality merchandise from over 600 world-famous brands in fashion, jewelry, cosmetics, perfumes and watches etc.</p>\n<p><br>\nThe Shilla Duty Free is the largest cosmetics &amp; perfumes duty free retailer in Incheon International Airport, and the company strives to expand the global business to serve customers in Asia.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>The Shilla Duty Free is the top beauty destination at Changi Airport with 23 Cosmetics and Perfumes stores across the four terminals including Shilla Beauty Loft, the world’s first duty free beauty services loft. The Shilla Duty Free also operates two watch boutiques, Maison de Chronus as well as Victoria’s Secret stores at Terminal 2 and Terminal 3.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>We are rapidly expanding our presence in travel retail!&nbsp;</p>",
